			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_64637433" name="comment_link_64637433" href="//it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23393533&amp;cid=64637433" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64637433)" >Re:The fix has been out for at least a few hours</a>


